</div>
</div>
<div class="docback">
<div class="note-source" id="TSJN-01-04-0455-sn"><p><abbr title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ file copy (applied to all forms of retained copies) ]">FC</abbr> (<span class="ref-rep" title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ Library of Congress ]">DLC</span>: <span class="ref-rep" title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ Papers of the Continental Congress ]">PCC</span>. No. 15); at head of text: Circular.</p>
<p>This circular to the states was drawn up by a committee of Congress which reported on 15 Jan. The draft report, in the hand of James Duane, is in <span class="ref-rep" title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ Library of Congress ]">DLC</span>: <span class="ref-rep" title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ Papers of the Continental Congress ]">PCC</span>, No. 24, and is printed in <span class="ref-st" title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ &lt;i&gt;Journals of the Continental Congress, 17741789&lt;/i&gt;, ed. W. C. Ford and others, Washington, 19041937 ]">JCC</span>, <span class="hi-small-caps" style="font-variant: small-caps;">xix</span>, 5861. See also <a href="default.xqy?keys=TSJN-print-01-03-02-0374" class="document">Samuel Huntington to TJ, 20 Mch.</a>, <a href="default.xqy?keys=TSJN-print-01-04-02-0081" class="document">26 Oct. (second letter)</a>, and <a href="default.xqy?keys=TSJN-print-01-04-02-0131" class="document">9 Nov. 1780</a>.</p></div>
